### Define RxDB Schema with One-to-Many Reference

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs-src/docs/population.md

Defines a schema for a collection with a 'friends' property that is an array of references to documents in the 'human' collection. This enables one-to-many relationships where a single document can link to multiple other documents.

