### Define RxDB Schema with One-to-One Reference

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs-src/docs/population.md

Defines a schema for a 'human' collection with a 'bestFriend' property that references another document in the same 'human' collection. The 'ref' keyword specifies the target collection, and the 'type' must be a string or array of strings representing the primary key of the referenced document.

```javascript
export const refHuman = {
    title: 'human related to other human',
    version: 0,
    primaryKey: 'name',
    properties: {
        name: {
            type: 'string'
        },
        bestFriend: {
            ref: 'human',     // refers to collection human
            type: 'string'    // ref-values must always be string or ['string','null'] (primary of foreign RxDocument) 
        }
    }
};

```

