### Add Humans Collection to RxDB Database

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/rx-storage-dexie.html

Defines and adds a 'humans' collection to the RxDB database with a specified schema. The schema includes fields for id, name, and age, with 'id' as the primary key.

```javascript
await db.addCollections({
  humans: {
    schema: {
      version: 0,
      type: 'object',
      primaryKey: 'id',
      properties: {
        id: { type: 'string', maxLength: 100 },
        name: { type: 'string' },
        age: { type: 'number' }
      },
      required: ['id', 'name']
    }
  }
});
```

